{{Infobox XC3 Enemy |name = Lavi Pagul |image = |caption = Lavi Pagul |category = [[Quest Exclusive Enemy (XC3)|Quest Exclusive]] [[Boss (XC3)|Boss]] |type = [[Pagul]] |level = 47 |area = [[Erythia Sea]] ([[Lavi Sandbar]]) |spawntime = During ''[[Romero and Joulietta]]'' |respawn = No |movement = |detection = |exp = |cp = |sp = }} The '''Lavi Pagul''' is a [[Quest Exclusive Enemy (XC3)|Quest Exclusive]] [[Boss (XC3)|Boss]] in {{XC3}}. It is a member of the [[Pagul]] family, and is fought at level 47 on [[Lavi Sandbar]] in [[Erythia Sea]] during ''[[Romero and Joulietta]]''. {{clr}}
