{{Infobox_NPC |name = Layla |image = XC3 Layla Icon.png |personality = |time_active = |gender = Female |race = [[Keves]]i human |age = 2nd Term |location = [[Eagus Wilderness]] ([[Colony 4]]) }} '''Layla''' is a NPC in {{XC3}}.
== Overview == Layla can be found in [[Colony 4]] after completing ''[[Side Story: Lanz]]''. She was part of [[Garvel]]'s squad alongside and a childhood rival of [[Noah]] and his friends at [[Colony 14]]. She died during the war with [[Agnus]] after moving to [[Colony 8]], and was later reborn as a soldier of [[H's Colony]] alongside Garvel and [[Hoope]]. After [[Lanz]] and the party defeat [[Consul]] [[H]], she is freed from the control of her Colony's [[Flame Clock]] and is sent to [[Colony 4]] before being transferred to [[Colony 9 (XC3)|Colony 9]]. {{clr}}
== Battle == {{Infobox XC3 Enemy |name = Layla |image = Team Garvel.png |caption = Layla |category = [[Quest Exclusive Enemy (XC3)|Quest Exclusive]] [[Boss (XC3)|Boss]] |type = Team Garvel |level = 47 |area = [[Great Sword's Base]] ([[Cradle Convoy Shelter]]) |spawntime = During ''[[Side Story: Lanz]]'' |respawn = No |movement = |detection = |exp = |wp = |sp = }} '''Layla''' is a [[Quest Exclusive Enemy (XC3)|Quest Exclusive]] [[Boss (XC3)|Boss]]. She is a [[Keves Forces|Keves Soldier]] who is fought at level 47 at the [[Cradle Convoy Shelter]] at the [[Great Sword's Base]] during ''[[Side Story: Lanz]]''. {{clr}}
